snippet.title: Jet Set Willy: The Lord of the Rings (Hard Version) walkthrough | ZX Spectrum | JSWCL-093
snippet.description:
A walkthrough of the Hard Version of "Jet Set Willy: The Lord of the Rings", a 2000 ZX Spectrum game by Andrew Broad.

The game's page on JSW Central is at https://jswcentral.org/jsw48-a-17_lotr.html.
